title: Thales Payshield 10K LMK
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/Payshield
license: Proprietary
distribution: Proprietary
description:
 This check monitors the status and details of loaded Local Master Keys (LMK) on a Thales Payshield HSM via SNMP. It reports the number of loaded, old, and test LMKs, and provides detailed information for each LMK slot, including authentication, scheme, algorithm, and check value.

 The check "Payshield LMK Num Old Loaded" is OK as long as there are 0 old LMKs loaded and is in WARN state if at least one old LMK is loaded. The check "Payshield LMK Num Test Loaded" is always OK and reports how many LMKs in mode "test" are loaded.

inventory:
 This check does not create inventory entries.

